items.headline: Welcome to Waterloo Road Wiki
items.desc: Waterloo Road Wiki is a fan-made website whose aim it is to to provide its visitors with detailed information on all the different aspects of BBC's Waterloo Road including episodes, characters, locations actors, etc. This wiki is fan-made which means that visitors can, and are encouraged, to join in and add any information about the series that they know.
